1. download binary
--> wget -c https://github.com/hyperledger/besu/releases/download/24.8.0/besu-24.8.0.zip -O besu.zip
--> unzip besu.zip

2. unzip and mv it to /opt
--> mv besu-24.8.0 /opt

3. add environment variable
--> nano .bashrc
--> export PATH=/opt/besu/bin:$PATH
-->source .bashrc

4. test the command
--> besu --help



[inspired from https://yehiatarek67.medium.com/install-hyperledger-besu-on-linux-for-beginners-a5a67d1f54c7]
